Copy the files in your .vim directory and add the following lines to your .vimrc

au BufRead,BufNewFile *.gm set filetype=gm
au BufRead,BufNewFile *.gr[gi] set filetype=grg
au BufRead,BufNewFile *.grs set filetype=grs

au! Syntax gm source $HOME/.vim/syntax/gm.vim
au! Syntax grg source $HOME/.vim/syntax/grg.vim
au! Syntax grs source $HOME/.vim/syntax/grs.vim

filetype plugin indent on

